#!/bin/bash
# List available ops commands.
cat <<'EOF'
Available ops commands (run from repo root):

  THE GATES
  ---------
  ops/check              Pre-commit gate (~20s warm). Runs test_ts +
                         test_elm + test_go. Every check inside is
                         <20s individually. Wired to git pre-commit
                         via ops/install-hooks.

  ops/check_full         Milestone gate (~50s warm). ops/check plus
                         test_full_game.ts (agent self-play, 6 seeds,
                         ~30s warm). Run before pushing changes that
                         touch the BFS engine, agent loop, or bucket
                         pipeline.

  ops/test_ts            Fast TS gate (~15s). Typecheck + every fast
                         TS test + dead-export scan.
  ops/test_elm           Fast Elm gate (~4s). Embed DSLs + standalone
                         typecheck + elm make + elm-test + elm-review.
  ops/test_go            Fast Go gate (~5s). go build ./...

  BUILD & RUN
  -----------
  ops/start              Start Gopher server (port 9000). Kills any
                         stale process, rebuilds the Go binary,
                         recompiles Elm bundles, waits until ready.
                         Do not replace with ad-hoc 'go run' — you
                         will skip those steps.

  ops/build_elm          Compile Game.elm + Puzzle.elm into elm.js and
                         puzzle.js. Calls ops/build_engine_js first.
                         Called automatically by ops/start.
  ops/build_engine_js    Bundle the TS engine into elm/engine.js via
                         esbuild. Run after any games/lynrummy/ts/
                         edit before testing the live Elm UI.

  REGEN & TOOLS
  -------------
  ops/embed_dsls_for_elm.ts   Embed .dsl scenarios into Lib.DslContent
                              for elm-test. Called by ops/test_elm.
  ops/find-dead-ts-exports    Report TS exports with no importing file.
                              Called by ops/test_ts.

  ops/install-hooks      One-time per clone: enable the tracked
                         pre-commit hook (sets core.hooksPath).
  ops/list               This screen.

Credentials convention: store in ~/AngryGopher/ (non-hidden, outside git).
EOF
